        <item>
            <title>Version 1.3.2</title>
            <sparkle:version>5</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in Plotted 1.3.2</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed: widgets now register with macOS again. Restored the App Sandbox entitlement on the widget extension, which is required for chronod to launch the extension. Heatmap, Tracker, Streak, Today, and Week-Compare widgets are usable from Notification Center and the desktop.</li>
                    <li>Properly code-signed with hardened runtime.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 30 Apr 2026 00:53:00 +0000</pubDate>
